snippet.title: Catalyst Black - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
The team battleground shooter set in a new world of powerful guns, customizable abilities, and mystical primals from another realm. Launching on iOS and Android globally on May 25th.

Pre-register now at 👉 https://catalystblack.com/ to unlock rewards!

Blog post: https://www.superevilmegacorp.com/catalyst-black-launching-may25/
